	double precision function dot(x, y)CC*******************************************************************************CC       Copyright (C) 1993, California Institute of Technology.  U.S.C       Government Sponsorhip under NASA Contract NAS7-918 isC       acknowledged.CC*******************************************************************************CC	computes vector dot product        double precision x(3), y(3)        dot = x(1)*y(1) + x(2)*y(2) + x(3)*y(3)        return        END